    p Help us make more wacky wizards and draw a wizard template! We may add it to the bot! Send a tweet to #[a(href='https://twitter.com/anywizard') #{title}]
    h2 More Info
    p #[a(href='http://hamburgersandwich.com') Matthew Rapati]
